@David_Ornstein : &ldquo;A lot will depend on whether Arsenal manage to move out the likes of Torreira, Guendouzi &amp; Sokratis. Roma expressed interest in signing Alexandre Lacazette but the amount they were prepared to pay fell comfortably below what Arsenal want.&rdquo; [ @TheAthleticUK ] #afc<br />
