The Partey situation is complicated by Atletico who insist his &euro;50m clause is activated &amp; would need to be paid in one go. The requested salary &amp; agent fees are steep with Arsenal unwilling to overpay. They have back-up targets should an agreement not be found. [ @David_Ornstein ]<br />
<br />
Aouar currently looks the more likely of the two, with Lyon needing to sell &amp; the player thought to be keen on joining Arsenal. Dialogue between Edu &amp; Juninho has been cordial. Arsenal do have other options if they cannot land Aouar. [ @David_Ornstein ] #afc <br />
<br />
